{"tid":1937873,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"知唔知點解俾狗咬左會搵唔返","createTime":"2020-03-22T07:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T02:48:59.000Z","uid":69221,"like":35,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f26b40fa31104d1dfbb4558a9a59ff67bb7113aa","tid":1937873,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:36:20.000Z","msg":"琴晚有個女手足係銅鑼灣被咬 唔好比佢消失<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1937693\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1937693</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n講左幾個月發夢要用鬼機，每日要secluded Message報平安，幾多人有做到？<br />\n如果真係有，就唔會一個二個冇消息，而係一定有人上黎講:我朋友XXX，講左琴日會去XXX，之後就失左蹤<br />\n<br />\n就算真係唔會搵得返都叫有證據有線索，可以推上美國be watwe act <br />\n<br />\n但係好明顯大部分人都懶，僥倖心理覺未必到自己，而啲狗玩完殺完見你地根本唔知邊個唔見咗，更加肆無忌憚<br />\n<br />\n啲狗嘅猖狂係你地造成<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有set<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇喎吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ddcada39835af766d2a2a4243bfc54c980a762","tid":1937873,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:38:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"052a847b94c65b7a3b7e967b2f609eb4095917fc","tid":1937873,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:40:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"507ea2d8652488dfd91fe9983bc3f405a0d1dba9","tid":1937873,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2stC8YY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2stC8YY.jpg&h=9f623ce2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb94aef1e142c1e0ad4cf28964e977c7ad83d04e","tid":1937873,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afd79df75ce23173b9254d1747b9ee3b03b3e614","tid":1937873,"uid":206047,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T07:43:28.000Z","msg":"「啲狗咁猖狂係你地造成」，你都on